title: StartHandFish
---
You've encountered Hand Fish! They have quite the austere appearance. Can't you tell?
<<set $fishName to "Hand Fish">>
{$fishName}: Hello.
<<set $step to 0>>
<<set $blubstep = 0>>
<<jump HandFishBattleMenu>>
