title: HandFishBattleMenu
---
-> > TALK <<if $step is 0>>
    <<jump HandFishTalk1>>
-> > TALK <<if $step is 1>>
    <<jump HandFishTalk2>>
-> > TALK <<if $step is 2>>
    <<jump HandFishTalk3>>
-> > TALK <<if $step is 3>>
    <<jump HandFishTalk4>>
-> > TALK <<if $step is 4>>
    <<jump HandFishTalk5>>    
-> > BUBBLE
    <<jump HandFishBubble>>
-> > BLUB
    <<jump HandFishBlub>>
-> > SWIM AWAY
    <<jump HandFishSwimAway>>
    
===

title: HandFishTalk1
---
-> > No Nonsense
    You: Will you come with me, help me get enough strength to contain What Lies Above
    {$fishName}: Ough, do I have to be that serious too? I don't know...
    <<lose_air 1>>
    <<jump HandFishBattleMenu>>
-> > Hand Pun
    You: Will you give me a hand in my journey to save the sea and sky?
    {$fishName}: Ha-ha! Good one! Do another!
    <<set $step = $step + 1>>
    <<lose_air 1>>
    <<jump HandFishBattleMenu>>
===

title: HandFishTalk2
