title: HandFishBlub
---
You: Blub blub.
<<if $blubstep is 0>>
    {$fishName}: Huh? What are you saying? I'm always ready to lend a hand, but I cant only do that if I can understand you!
<<elseif $blubstep is 1>>
    {$fishName}: Cmon, gimme a hand here!
<<else>>
    {$fishName}: Sigh, this has gotten out of hand.
<<endif>>
<<set $blubstep = $blubstep + 1>>
<<jump HandFishBattleMenu>>
===

title: HandFishSwimAway
---
You: I can't handle this anymore. 
{$fishName}: Ha! Maybe another time.
<<jump Leave>>

===